Use the radio buttons and check boxes to visualize 2016 and 2020 Election Results by County.

Land Circles are drawn to match the land area of each county
Population Circles are drawn to match the relative population of each county
No County Overlap will arrange the circles so you can see them all
Color by Margin will color the circles by vote margin
When circles are drawn, hover over each county to see election results
